	<h1 class="title">1100 万美元奖金！电玩也可以玩成“大联盟”了</h1>
	<div class="author-date clearfix">					
			<div class="author clearfix">
					<span class="avatar x25 circle">
						<img src="/img/missing_face.png" alt="">
					</span>
				<span class="name">NICK WINGFIELD</span>
			</div>
		<span class="date smart-date" data-originDate="2014-09-09 08:08:43 +0800"></span>
	</div>
	<div class="banner">
			<img src="/system/articles/articleshows/2183/medium/2183.jpg?1436648658" alt="" />			
	</div>
